# GraphQL API Module

{{ project_name }} includes a GraphQL API built with [Strawberry](https://strawberry.rocks/).

## Quick Start

```bash
# Start the GraphQL server
uv run uvicorn {{ package_name }}.graphql:app --reload
```

## GraphQL Playground

Access the GraphQL playground at `http://localhost:8000/graphql`.

## Schema

The GraphQL schema is defined in `src/{{ package_name }}/graphql/schema.py`.

## Queries

```graphql
query {
  hello
}
```

## Mutations

```graphql
mutation {
  createItem(input: { name: "Example" }) {
    id
    name
  }
}
```

## Testing

```bash
# Run GraphQL tests
uv run pytest tests/graphql/
```

